Preserve absolute guest paths for chown and lchown host imports.

The host_fs ownership ABI accepts UINT32_MAX as the cwd/absolute-path sentinel.
Resolving through wasi-libc preopens before the import lost the mount prefix in
the V8 runner, turning /mnt/test/link into /link.

